race.description: Join The Club - Become A Member Hcp (C3)
race.comment: Tough race to finish with the majority coming off last start failures. SNIP OF GOSSIP (5) has an excuse at least having pulled up lame last start when at the tail over a mile at Northam. Form prior was good for this and gets chance to atone. SIDE SHOW (13) also had good form going into last start then finished at the tail at Belmont. Doesn't win out of turn but well placed here and should be winding up late if back on track. RUNFORROB (6) was a winner here two back then gave away too big a start in town and never in it. INVINCIBLE RUBY (2) is been going better than it looks. Has been run off her legs and getting home hard when the race is all over this time in. Steps out in trip now and can run into the finish. WORCESTER (1) has been mixing form lately but did win only try here at a similar distance and gets chance to atone.
